data.description: Immaculate Charleston-style home with great curb appeal. This first floor Master home has an open floor plan with a spacious & bright kitchen and living space. The kitchen is perfect for cooking and entertaining with traffic flow directly into the dining and living room. Huge master downstairs with soaking tub, over-sized tiled shower, granite counters and large closet. Upstairs find two bedrooms with a large porch off both for more outdoor space. Included upstairs is a well appointed loft space that could be used as an additional living area or office. Screened in porch off the back of the house is a perfect place to escape. Full laundry room/mud room and two car garage round this house out nicely. This home has many builder upgrades and seller has made many more during ownership Cont; Great landscaping and hardscaping all around the house, plantation shutters throughout the house and beautiful Bahama style hurricane shutters outside. This house is just steps away from a 25 acre lake with dock and fire-pits of the Whitney Lake community.
